    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Chromatographic technique used in analysis of alkyds in which pyrolysis is effected in the presence of an alkaline reagent. The technique was developed to identify the components in these polymers (oil-modified polyesters), rates of cross-linking, and mechanical properties.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
